extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      .one-page-sidebar
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          .one-page-logo
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_regional')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/hr_regional')
              img(src='/images/regional.png')
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li.is-active
              a(href='#intro')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-info
                | Introduction
            li
              a(href='#dashboard')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-dashboard
                | Dashboard
            li
              a(href='#jobs')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-black-tie
                | Jobs
            li
              a(href='#resumes')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-file
                | Resumes
            li
              a(href='#employees')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user
                | Employees
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        br
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
              .col-md-9.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_regional')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a.active(href='/hr_regional/introduction') Introduction 
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_regional/manager') HR Manager
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_regional/header') Header
                    li
                      a(href='/hr_regional/settings') Settings
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              #intro.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Introduction
                p.category-content
                  | Hr Regional is the resource who will divide the regions and assign HR Managers based on  city-wise. Furthermore, HR Manager will have the admin access in SkilledTree.
                  | .
            .col-md-12
              br
              // Category Info
              #dashboard.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Dashboard
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | It’s a data visualization tool which helps you to get the complete details of the number of employees, number of cities, number of jobs posted and number of referral candidate resumes uploaded based on city-wise.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/regionaldashboard3.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/regionaldashboard2.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              br
              #jobs.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1 Jobs
                p.category-content
                  | Jobs which are posted in all the cities which you have created will be listed along with the department where the job belongs to, referral bonus details and job description. You can share those jobs in any of your social media accounts such as Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter, Email Client etc., by clicking on the job title.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/regionjobs.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              br
              #resumes.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Resumes
                p.category-content
                  | You can check the resume repository that provides few details such as candidate name, job which they have applied, their skillset, the referrer who referred them and the date on which they have applied to the job for in the ‘Resumes’ page.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/regionresumes.png', width='100%')
            br
            br
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #employees.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Employees
                p.category-content
                  | You can check the employees list that provides few details such as Emp ID, Name of the employee, Team they belong to, number of their friends network, Last logged in date and their contact information
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/regionalresumes.png', width='100%')
    // End of One Page Content
